# ── Rust build artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────
/target/
**/*.pdb

# ── Compiled distributions (publish via GitHub Releases) ─────────
/dist/

# ── EvoCLI runtime data — any depth (never commit) ────────────────
**/.evocli/
*.fast
*.fieldnorm
*.idx
*.pos
*.store
*.term
.tantivy-meta.lock
.tantivy-writer.lock

# ── Backup / temp files ────────────────────────────────────────────
*.bak
*.orig
*.tmp

# ── Debug / trace output files ────────────────────────────────────
tracer_*.txt

# ── SQLite databases ───────────────────────────────────────────────
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# ── Python cache ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
*.egg-info/
build/
.eggs/
.coverage
.coverage.*
htmlcov/

# ── IDE / editor ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── OS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── Secrets — never commit API keys ───────────────────────────────
*.env
.env*
secrets.toml

# ── Large binary assets ────────────────────────────────────────────
*.exe
*.bin
*.so
*.dylib
*.dll

# ── AI tool context / plugin files (not needed for development) ───
# These are specific to individual AI coding assistants and contain
# session context, plugin configs, or internal progress tracking.
# Reference: docs/config.toml.example for actual configuration.
STATUS.md
CLAUDE.md
GEMINI.md
AGENTS.md
**/AGENTS.md
opencode.json
package.json
plugin.json
.claude-plugin/
.codex-plugin/
.cursor-plugin/
docs/GAP_ANALYSIS.md

